    <title>朴素想法在实际中的应用</title>
    <link href="http://www.zpure.xyz/2020/03/11/simple-philosophy-apply/"/>
    <id>http://www.zpure.xyz/2020/03/11/simple-philosophy-apply/</id>
    <published>2020-03-11T02:57:20.000Z</published>
